دد","pos":"V","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1201","n1202","","n38321"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1201","headword_ar":"امّد","root":"Amd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^omiydN","text_ar":"تَاْمِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He declared the time, considered with regard to its end;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the utmost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extreme, extent, term, limit, point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reach;"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bay~ana AlA^amada","text_ar":"بَيَّنَ الاَمَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n1202","headword_ar":"اَمَدٌ","root":"Amd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time, considered with regard to its end:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamaAnN","text_ar":"زَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being time considered with regard to its end and its beginning: (Er-Rághib:) [but sometimes it is interchangeable with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamaAnN","text_ar":"زَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as will be seen in what follows:] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utmost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extreme, extent, term, limit, point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reach."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga A^amadahu","text_ar":"بَلَغَ اَمَدَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, reached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attained, his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its, utmost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extreme, extent, term,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba lahu A^amadFA","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ لَهُ اَمَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He assigned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appointed, for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, a term,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa baEiydu AlA=maAdi","text_ar":"هُوَ بَعِيدُ الا=مَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is one whose limits are remote:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=maAdN","text_ar":"ا=مَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being the pl.]. (A.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"period of life which one has reached;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^amaduka","text_ar":"مَا اَمَدُكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is thy period of life which thou hast reached?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Each of the two terms of the life"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man; i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time of"},{"kind":"text","text":"his"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"birth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time of"},{"kind":"text","text":"his"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, T.) El-Hasan [El-Basree], being asked by El-Hajjáj,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^amaduka","text_ar":"مَا اَمَدُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What was the time of thy birth?"},{"kind":"text","text":"answered by saying that it was two years before the expiration of 'Omar's reign as Khaleefeh. (T, L, from a trad.) ―         -b4-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"startingplace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of horses in a race. (Sh, T, L.) ―         -b5-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any space of time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a space of time of unknown limit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull pp. 9 and 10.) ―         -b6-  Sometimes, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A particular time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amadu ka*aA","text_ar":"اَمَدُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The time of such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamaAnu A^amadN","text_ar":"زَمَانُ اَمَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Kull p. 10.) ―         -b7-  [It is also used for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*w A^amadN","text_ar":"ذو اَمَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and (applied to a fem. n.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAt A^amadK","text_ar":"ذَات اَمَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having a term,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limit; limited in duration;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~unoyaA A^amadN wAlA=xirpu A^abadN","text_ar":"الدُّنْيَا اَمَدٌ والا=خِرةُ اَبَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The present state of existence is limited in duration, but the final state of existence is everlasting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Obeyd Ibn-'Omeyr, L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abd","text_ar":"ابد"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n38321","headword_ar":"اَمَدُّ","root":"md","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most tall, high, long,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa mino A^amad~i Aln~aAsi qaAmapF","text_ar":"هُوَ مِنْ اَمَدِّ النَّاسِ قَامَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is of the tallest of men in stature."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEamo waA^a$ad~ahu waA^amad~ahu","text_ar":"نَعَمْ وَاَشَدَّهُ وَاَمَدَّهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Yes: even the utmost thereof, and the most that could be thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"Said in reply to the question “ Hast thou done it? ” (A.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amad~u SawotFA","text_ar":"اَمَدُّ صَوْتًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Higher"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"louder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highest"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loudest, of voice."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lqY","text_ar":"لقى"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["A"]}]}}